=== Installation instructions for Smarty ===
Download Smarty from http://www.smarty.net/download

Copy the contents of the 'libs/' directory into this directory

Create the directories 'cache', 'configs' and 'templates_c' manually

On my system the following files are now in this directory:

cache
configs
debug.tpl
plugins
README
Smarty.class.php
sysplugins
templates
templates_c
